    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Patris et Filii et Spiritu Sancti. Anno Deo propitjo pontificato
                        domni nostris <persName key="#Popes" ref="#people/1572"
                            >Ioh(anni)s</persName> summi pontifitjs et universali <rs key="#Popes"
                            >pape</rs> in apostolica sacratissima beati Petri apostoli Domini sede
                        anno quarto, regnate donnus <persName key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/130"
                            >Enricus</persName> inclitus <rs key="#Emperor/king">res</rs> in Italia
                        anno quinto in Dei nomine, die viesimo m(ense) aprelis, ind(itjone) sexta,
                        in loco qui vocatur <placeName ref="#places/3544">Arquada</placeName>, <rs
                            key="#Plebs">plebem</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Plebs" ref="#juridical_persons/1496">Sancti Andrei</orgName>.
                        Petistis ad me in Dei nomine donnus <persName key="#Other_clerics #Abbots"
                            ref="#people/1560">Gariadus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">clericus</rs> et <rs key="#Abbots">abas</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">mo(nasterii)</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Fundi #Casalia #Fluvial_transport #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Legumes #Wine #Acorns #Hay/fodder #Eggs #Linen #Pigs #Poultry #Exenia #Levies #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1474">Sancte Marie qui vocatur in
                            Senedochio</orgName> uti vobis in Dei nomine <persName><name
                                ref="Iohannes">Ioh(anne)s</name></persName> filio quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Ursa">Ursa</name></persName> in omnia
                        medietatem de omnes <rs key="#Landed_possessions">sortes et pertinentja</rs>
                        que fuit de <persName key="#Deacons"><name ref="Natalis"
                            >Natale</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Deacons">diagonus</rs> filio quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Dominicus/Montanario">Dominicus Montanario</name></persName>,
                        in alia autem medietate abead <persName><name ref="Ursa"
                            >Ursa</name></persName> et <persName><name ref="Lula"
                            >Lula</name></persName> et <persName><name ref="Maria"
                            >Maria</name></persName> se(h)u filiis earum – in tali vero tenore
                        qualis de ipsi petitoris sine eredes mortuus fuerit cadat ad ipsi que
                        superviserit – libell(ario) nomine concedimus et larimus seo confirmamus de
                        rem iuris nostre mo(nasterii) Sancte Marie in Senedochio, idest tota et in
                        integra vel omnes sortes et portjones quantacumque abet detinet Natale
                        diagonus in totum <rs key="#Fundi">fundo</rs> qui vocatur <geogName
                            key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Fundi #Casalia #Fluvial_transport #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Legumes #Wine #Acorns #Hay/fodder #Eggs #Linen #Pigs #Poultry #Exenia #Levies #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            ref="#estates/2441"><placeName
                                key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Fundi #Casalia #Fluvial_transport #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Legumes #Wine #Acorns #Hay/fodder #Eggs #Linen #Pigs #Poultry #Exenia #Levies #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                                ref="#places/4181">Villa Martjana</placeName></geogName>, idest: ab
                        uno llatere <rs key="#Confinia #Canals">fosato qui vocatur de Corgnaria</rs>
                        et secundo llatere <rs key="#Pagus">pagino</rs> qui vocatur de <placeName
                            key="#Confinia #Pagus">Breusi</placeName> et tertjo llatere <rs
                            key="#Confinia">gorizo qui vocatur Auriagni</rs> et quarto llatere <rs
                            key="#Confinia #Canals">fosato de valle qui vocatur Loudegna</rs>; ec
                        omnia cum <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs> et <rs key="#Wine"
                            >vineis</rs>, <rs key="#Cereals">campis</rs>, <rs key="#Hay/fodder"
                            >pratis</rs>, <rs key="#Hay/fodder">pascuis</rs>, <rs key="#Forests"
                            >silvis</rs>, <rs>salecti</rs>, <rs key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos"
                            >padulibus</rs>, <rs key="#Fisheries">piscatjonibus</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">venatjonibus</rs> et
                        constituto <rs key="#Fines">territorio</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Fines" ref="#estates/2420"><placeName key="#Fines"
                                ref="#places/3522">Adrienssi</placeName></geogName>, <rs
                            key="#Plebs">plebem</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Plebs" ref="#juridical_persons/1486">Sancti
                        Stefani</orgName>; ec omnia concedimus vobis suprascripti petitoris se(h)u
                        filiis vestris abendum, tenendum, laborandum, pastinandum, rongandum,
                        capelandum, pasculandum, supersedendum, defensandum, i omnibus meliorandum,
                        in annis advenientibus viinti et nove ad renovandum. Ita sanead ut inferatis
                        domnice ratjonibus vobis vestresque filiis de quitquit in ibidem Dominus
                        omnem annualiter donare dingnatus fuerit, <rs key="#Levies">terratigo</rs>
                        dare debeatis: de <rs key="#Cereals #Maiores">grano</rs> in capo capa quarta
                        et <rs key="#Cereals #Maiores">sicale</rs> in capo capa quinta et <rs
                            key="#Legumes">faba</rs> in area modio quinto et <rs key="#Cereals"
                            >mesturia ingranata</rs> in capo capa quinta, <rs
                            key="#Cereals #Minores">trisigo</rs>, <rs key="#Cereals #Minores"
                            >mileo</rs>, <rs key="#Cereals #Minores">pagnigo</rs> in area modio
                        octavo, traenda et tritulando per vos petitoris, et <rs key="#Linen"
                            >lino</rs> magnipula detjma gramulata; et si vinea pastinaveritis fruere
                        debeatis post intorta pervenerit annis nove et postea redere debeatis sicut
                        de ceterra terra; <rs key="#Exenia">exenio</rs> vero pro <rs
                            key="#Casalia #Size">casale treinta perticas in longo et viinti in
                            lato</rs> dare debeatis <rs key="#Poultry">pullo</rs> uno et <rs
                            key="#Eggs">oves</rs> quinque; si <rs key="#Acorns">glande</rs>
                        abueritis de potj decem <rs key="#Pigs">porgo</rs> uno; et non abeatis
                        licentja de suprascripta res ad nullo platjto neque distrita andare nisi ad
                        me suprascripto patrone et meis subcessoribus; pervectum omnem terratico
                        domnico per vos suprascripti petitoris usque ad <rs key="#Fluvial_transport">nave nostra domnica</rs> potuerit
                        pervenire. Maiore quidem domnico vestro vel vestra dominatjone cum onore et
                        obedientja susipere debeatis, ec omnia sine dolo vel fraude. Et si quis vero
                        pars vestra contra os libellum ire temtaverimus et omnia que superius
                        legitur non observaverimus vel adinpleverimus et contra ec ire, agere vel
                        contedere aut minuere voluero per quemlibet modum vel titulum ante
                        perfinitum tempus sicut superius legitur, det pars parte fide servante ante
                        omnis litis initjum aut interpell(atj)onis pene nomine <rs key="#Penalty"
                            >auri obtimi untj due</rs> et post penam soluta manentem os libello in
                        suo omnium robore et firmitatis. Quos vero libello uno pari tenore
                        conscripto <persName key="#Tabellio" ref="#people/1580">Liuperto</persName>
                        in Dei nomine <rs key="#Tabellio">tabell(ionem)</rs> huius <rs
                            key="#Comitatus">comitato</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/2435"><placeName key="#Comitatus"
                                ref="#places/3538">Gavell(ensi)</placeName></geogName> scribendum
                        rogavimus et subter manus mea propria firmavimus et unus alterius nobis
                        pariter contradimus, quod quotsecuti est Deum agatis [et] nobis maxima
                        gr(atj)a. Signum suprascripti Ioh(anne)s et Ursa et Lula et Maria germa(ni)
                        petitoris ad omnia suprascripta cui relectum est.</ab>
                </div>
